ed="T" n="0861a01"/><persName key="A013530">釋懷德</persName>，本<placeName key="PL000000000122">江南</placeName>人也。髫年離俗<ptr target="#n2957"/>，謹愿飾身，<lb
ed="T" n="0861a02"/>誦通《法華經》，得度。自爾雖登講肆，終以誦<lb
ed="T" n="0861a03"/>持為專務。晚遊<placeName key="PL000000010633">泗上</placeName>，<anchor xml:id="beg0861sgsz1"/>禮<anchor xml:id="end0861sgsz1"/><persName key="A011303">僧伽</persName>塔像。屬<ref type="person" target="#A001640">今上</ref><lb
ed="T" n="0861a04"/>遣高品<persName key="A019466">李神福</persName>齎<anchor xml:id="beg0861sgsz3"/>旙華<anchor xml:id="end0861sgsz3"/>上供，并感應舍利<lb
ed="T" n="0861a05"/>至，葬于新塔下基深窟中<ptr target="#n2958"/>。<persName key="A013530">德</persName>遂誓焚軀供<lb
ed="T" n="0861a06"/>養。先罄捨衣囊，供身之物齋僧一中<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1949"/>。然後<lb
ed="T" n="0861a07"/>自衣紙服，身纏油蠟，<anchor xml:id="beg0861sgsz5"/>禮<anchor xml:id="end0861sgsz5"/>辭僧眾，手持雙燭，<lb
ed="T" n="0861a08"/>登柴𧂐中，發火誦經。觀者莫不揮涕。<persName key="A013530">德</persName><lb
ed="T" n="0861a09"/>至火熾熛高，其身聊側，猶微聞誦經之聲。<lb
ed="T" n="0861a10"/>一城之人無不悲悼者。淘汰舍利甚多，乃<lb
ed="T" n="0861a11"/><date key="j20802402080240" when-iso="+0983-05-27"><name>太平興國</name>八年四月八日</date>也。<ref type="person" target="#A019466">使臣</ref>回奏，<ref type="person" target="#A001640">上</ref>為<lb
ed="T" n="0861a12"/>之動容焉。</p><milestone unit="page" rend="pagebreak"/>
